00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,240
Constable Qin.

2
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,960
Same MO again.

3
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,360
How many is it?

4
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,480
The third one.

5
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:06,560
The body was found by the night watchman,

6
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,960
but he didn't see the suspect's face.

7
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,600
Also strangled to death.

8
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:15,360
There was a fierce struggle before death.

9
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:21,160
The time of death should be the Hour of the Dog tonight.

10
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,079
By the way,

11
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,260
I remember the night of the first murder.

12
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,579
Was it raining too?

13
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,680
Yes, it was a rainy night.

14
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,420
The suspect always strikes on rainy nights.

15
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,680
The victims are all young women,

16
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,930
and none were sexually assaulted.

17
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:48,040
After suffocating to death,

18
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,120
they were tied with red ropes

19
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,020
on their backs,

20
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,840
had the same talisman drawn

21
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:54,540
and were left at the scene.

22
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,900
Constable Qin.

23
00:02:58,200 --> 00:03:00,530
The victims this time are all adult women.

24
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,880
In cases like this,

25
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,440
we all know

26
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:06,600
the culprit is usually a rapist or a thief.

27
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,320
But all the female victims this time

28
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,500
weren't sexually assaulted.

29
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,010
Instead, they died a tragic death.

30
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,360
I think

31
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:19,040
this suspect must have a huge grudge against women.

32
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:29,490
To be able to strangle someone to death with a thick hemp rope

33
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:32,160
and commit three murders in a row without being discovered,

34
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,920
the suspect is likely a single person,

35
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,160
physically strong,

36
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,160
and an adult male.

37
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,280
Around 20 years old.

38
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,610
Look, everyone.

39
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:48,920
From the three locations where the bodies were found, we can be sure

40
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,850
that the suspect

41
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:54,420
is extremely familiar with the route from the city gate to the back alley,

42
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:57,520
and then to the South Market Pier.

43
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,360
Then

44
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,360
we can narrow down the scope

45
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,960
and focus on investigating single men living alone in this area.

46
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,690
Understood.

47
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,880
Don't worry, Constable Qin.

48
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,320
We'll take action right away.

49
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,120
Yes.

50
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:09,840
Wait a minute.

51
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,400
Recently, on any rainy night,

52
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,640
we must increase patrols

53
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,920
and send more constables

54
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,880
to prevent the suspect from striking again.

55
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,440
I know.

56
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,800
Bring me my sword.

57
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,000
At that time, we deployed more manpower

58
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,600
and searched door-to-door.

59
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,800
Single men living alone

60
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,760
became our prime suspects.

61
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,159
It was raining continuously then.

62
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,890
Whenever it rained,

63
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:37,159
we would patrol the whole city at night.

64
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,440
But after searching for several days in a row,

65
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,800
we found nothing.

66
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,800
I remember it was sunny that day.

67
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,960
Constable Qin judged that it probably wouldn't rain again that night.

68
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:50,159
Also, because we had been patrolling during the day

69
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:51,200
and on duty at night for days,

70
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,600
everyone was exhausted.

71
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,740
Constable Qin prepared a banquet

72
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,040
for us to have a good drink

73
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,920
and relax.

74
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,930
But who would have thought,

75
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:01,560
the killer struck again that night.

76
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,520
It's like this again. The same as last time.

77
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,640
It's him again. It's terrifying.

78
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,770
I don't understand.

79
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,580
It didn't rain last night.

80
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,320
Why did the killer change his habit?

81
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,480
Rain might be a condition for the murder,

82
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:30,080
but not a necessary one.

83
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:34,180
The suspect always commits crimes on rainy nights.

84
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,540
It's highly likely

85
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,420
that it's related to his line of work.

86
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,370
Because of the rain,

87
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,520
he gets off work early and goes home,

88
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,800
giving him time to commit the crime.

89
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,960
Let me in!

90
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:55,600
Let me in!

91
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,720
Who are you?

92
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,960
Let me in!

93
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,120
He's the brother of the victim, Wang Chun.

94
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,920
He was present during the attack

95
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:06,280
and identified the killer as a man,

96
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:09,640
though he didn't see the face clearly.

97
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,080
What's your name?

98
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,240
Wang Mang.

99
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,130
Officer, Wang Chun is my older sister.

100
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:24,120
I heard she died a tragic death.

101
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,240
But

102
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,200
I still want to see her one last time.

103
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,940
Aren't you afraid?

104
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,540
Wang Chun is my sister.

105
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,250
I wouldn't be afraid of her no matter what.

106
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,680
How tragic.

107
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:56,760
Officer,

108
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,720
my sister was murdered.

109
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:01,090
Please, you must catch the killer.

110
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,480
I'm begging you.

111
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,040
Rest assured,

112
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,160
we will get justice for your sister.

113
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,490
It's been so many years,

114
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:22,240
and these cold cases remain unsolved.

115
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:26,050
If the killer from back then was never caught,

116
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,040
it's highly likely he'll strike again.

117
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,320
But we can't rule out

118
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,720
a copycat killer.

119
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,960
We can't just assume it's the same person

120
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,920
just because the MO is similar.

121
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,580
It must be the same person.

122
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,240
Look,

123
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,880
this red hemp rope,

124
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,860
the strange binding posture,

125
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:46,120
and the mysterious talisman on the back.

126
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,840
It's exactly the same as the original suspect.

127
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,980
You said Wang Mang saw the suspect back then.

128
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,440
Is he still alive?

129
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,120
He's alive.

130
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,320
Take me to him.

131
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,480
We've reached the pier.

132
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,410
It's just ahead.

133
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,360
Wang Mang.

134
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,160
Wang Mang, come here.

135
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,520
Constable Su.

136
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,520
Constable Su, any news on the suspect?

137
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,680
We haven't found the suspect,

138
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,120
but we have some other news.

139
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,780
Come, let's sit down and talk.

140
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,640
Constable Su.

141
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:38,440
Today, we found a female corpse in the East Market.

142
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,080
The victim's name is Qiuhua.

143
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,159
The killer's MO

144
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:48,960
matches the one used to kill your sister, Wang Chun.

145
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,370
Why are you smiling?

146
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,650
For all these years,

147
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,160
my biggest fear was that he had settled down

148
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,600
and would never commit another murder.

149
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,840
If that were the case,

150
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,580
I'd never get the chance to find out who he is.

151
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:12,250
So every night I've been thinking,

152
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,400
as long as he dares to strike again,

153
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,800
I'll definitely have a chance to catch him.

154
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,560
When Wang Chun was killed,

155
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,770
you saw the suspect.

156
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:25,800
Can you tell me the details of what happened back then?

157
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,610
What happened that day,

158
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,720
I will never forget.

159
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,720
Brother, why have you become so unreasonable?

160
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,380
You lied to me, sister.

161
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:48,200
You promised that if we sold all the radishes,

162
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,000
you'd buy me sugar-coated haws.

163
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,360
Mother is still sick at home.

164
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,600
We barely have enough to eat.

165
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:56,640
Why do other children have food

166
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,720
but I don't?

167
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,000
I worked harder than them.

168
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,560
Come, get up.

169
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,680
All right.

170
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,000
Come here.

171
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,240
Mang.

172
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,290
I'll buy one.

173
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,720
I won't eat.

174
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,280
You are the best, sister.

175
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,100
There are five haws on a stick.

176
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,880
We can have two each.

177
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:28,400
And save one for Mother.

178
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,800
Mang, slow down.

179
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,650
Here you go, little boy.

180
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,280
Thank you.

181
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,960
I want this one.

182
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:46,680
Sister!

183
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:57,160
The masked man held a wooden stick in his left hand.

184
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,620
He should be left-handed.

185
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,440
About six feet tall.

186
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,360
If I had listened to my sister

187
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,600
and gone home with her

188
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:10,200
instead of buying those sugar-coated haws,

189
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,640
she might not have died.

190
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:13,610
Then why didn't he kill you?

191
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,320
Wang Mang.

192
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:15,040
Yes.

193
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,520
Constable Su, I'm going to work.

194
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,800
Okay, go ahead.

195
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,720
If the suspect was seen by him,

196
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:27,240
it's highly possible that the suspect's dominant hand has changed.

197
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:30,370
So this can't be used as a characteristic of the suspect.

198
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:34,240
It was lucky for him to survive.

199
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,840
It wasn't luck.

200
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:36,640
First,

201
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,720
he didn't see the masked man's face,

202
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,360
so naturally he wouldn't be silenced.

203
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:40,920
Second,

204
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:41,800
look.

205
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:44,120
The victims are all women now.

206
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:47,640
Is it possible that women are his target

207
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,810
and he is not interested in men?

208
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:52,760
This masked man,

209
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,560
does his family sell masks?

210
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,960
I thought of that too.

211
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,920
Back then,

212
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:02,160
I checked all the vendors selling masks.

213
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,130
There were no suspects.

214
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,280
For so many years,

215
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:08,000
I've been thinking.

216
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,560
Every time after committing a crime,

217
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,420
the culprit would pose the bodies

218
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,660
in all kinds of strange postures.

219
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,520
And he used cinnabar

220
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:21,080
to write strange spells on the victims' backs.

221
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,440
There must be a purpose.

222
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,040
I've heard of

223
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:27,880
a ritual

224
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,690
that can resurrect people.

225
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,080
Could it be that the culprit

226
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,960
held a ritual to resurrect

227
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,480
his dead loved ones?

228
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:38,650
If it was for resurrection,

229
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:41,000
why did he wait 27 years to commit crimes again?

230
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,600
Right.

231
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,880
Maybe 27 years ago,

232
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:49,640
he successfully resurrected his loved ones,

233
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,400
so he stopped.

234
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:54,840
And 27 years later, someone close to him died again,

235
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:58,720
so he wants to do it all over again.

236
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,850
According to what you said,

237
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:05,080
more people will die.

238
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,720
Let go of me.

239
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,000
Let me go.

240
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:12,840
Let me go.

241
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:40,280
This is the archive room.

242
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,770
Are all the case files here?

243
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:44,960
Of course.

244
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,340
Don't mess around.

245
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,260
The file we are looking for is over there.

246
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:00,520
See?

247
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:04,580
These are the files left by Head Catcher Qin from his cases.

248
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:07,000
Head Catcher Qin had a characteristic:

249
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:10,160
he never forgot any case he handled,

250
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:12,860
and he would record them in complete detail.

251
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,920
Come, look.

252
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:19,050
Head Catcher Qin was a meticulous person.

253
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,440
Not only did he have an extraordinary memory,

254
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:23,370
but he was also skilled at drawing.

255
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:26,240
He would draw the crime scene every time

256
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,880
for future reference.

257
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:31,560
These were all drawn by Head Catcher Qin.

258
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,400
Of course.

259
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,840
Do you still remember how Qiuhua looked when she died?

260
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,200
Yes.

261
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:45,840
Find a portraitist to draw another one.

262
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,100
I want to compare them.

263
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,520
I can draw that too.

264
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,130
Head Catcher Su.

265
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:56,760
We found another body at the East Market crossing.

266
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:58,290
The MO is the same as before.

267
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:00,220
It was done by the same person.

268
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,520
This is Uncle Liang's house.

269
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:31,040
Alright, arrange some people to set up a defense outside.

270
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,720
Yes.

271
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:35,970
Uncle Liang.

272
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,010
Uncle Liang.

273
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:46,580
This is Head Catcher Su, Coroner Li, and Envoy Jueming from the yamen.

274
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,340
Let's go in and take a look.

275
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,480
Alright, let's go check the body first.

276
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,560
The deceased is named Liang Chuyi,

277
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,960
Uncle Liang's only daughter.

278
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,680
Liang Chuyi.

279
00:15:58,680 --> 00:15:59,560
She was married

280
00:15:59,680 --> 00:16:01,540
and they had a daughter together,

281
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:03,740
who is over eight years old this year.

282
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:21,180
The deceased is wearing only a red bellyband on her upper body.

283
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:23,600
Her whole body is entangled with red thread.

284
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:26,480
Her head and hands are suspended,

285
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,640
and her legs are kneeling on the table,

286
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:29,440
like a puppet.

287
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,360
Her face is pale

288
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,400
and her eyes are scarlet.

289
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:39,490
On the deceased's back,

290
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:42,530
there are incantations drawn with cinnabar.

291
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:44,800
The livor mortis is quite obvious.

292
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:47,330
The time of death is more than eight hours ago.

293
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:51,680
There is a strangulation mark of about one cun on the neck,

294
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,140
appearing purplish-red.

295
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:55,640
The initial judgement of the cause of death

296
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,920
should be strangulation leading to asphyxiation,

297
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,720
and then posed in this bizarre manner after death.

298
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:03,680
Although it looks similarly bizarre,

299
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:06,560
the method is somewhat different.

300
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:07,720
the method is somewhat different.

301
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:11,640
Look, the body is in a kneeling state of atonement.

302
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,119
Although her facial expression is in great pain,

303
00:17:14,119 --> 00:17:15,450
