310
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,160
After being fixed for a period of time,

311
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:54,360
the muscles would form a rigor mortis in the new position,

312
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:57,380
thus maintaining this smiling appearance.

313
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,160
Let me go.

314
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:08,320
Did Qiuhua have a wooden stick in her mouth?

315
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:08,920
No.

316
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:28,240
The deceased's body

317
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:31,320
