321
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:44,360
Did your daughter have asthma?

322
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,440
My little grandson does.

323
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:52,240
Is your grandson at home?

324
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,360
Yesterday,

325
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:59,490
