326
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:02,440
My son-in-law happened to be working outside.

327
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:04,640
So my youngest daughter was home alone.

328
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:06,840
This morning,

329
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:08,360
